          <name xml:lang="en">price</name>
          <unitName xml:lang="en">EUR2005</unitName>
          <comment xml:lang="en">Price calculated based on price of elemental sulfur (f.o.b. mine or plant) reported in the USGS Minerals Yearbook for Sulfur from 2010 to 2019 (https://www.usgs.gov/centers/nmic/sulfur-statistics-and-information). The prices given in USD were converted to EUR based on the annual exchange rates published by the European Central Bank (https://sdw.ecb.europa.eu/quickview.do?SERIES_KEY=120.EXR.A.USD.EUR.SP00.A), and then adjusted for inflation relative to 2005 by using the Harmonised Index of Consumer Prices (HICP) of the euro area, published by eurostat (https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/databrowser/view/PRC_HICP_AIND/default/table).</comment>
        </property>
